<section class="pd-24">
  <st-panel>
    <a-row :gutter="24">
      <a-col :span="9">
        <st-info>
          <st-info-item label="配送方式">
            {{ info.shipping_mode_name }}
          </st-info-item>
          <st-info-item label="快递单号" v-if="info.shipping_sn">
            {{ info.shipping_sn }}
          </st-info-item>
          <st-info-item label="操作人">
            {{ info.operator }}
          </st-info-item>
        </st-info>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="9">
        <st-info>
          <st-info-item label="快递公司" v-if="info.company_name">
            {{ info.company_name }}
          </st-info-item>
          <st-info-item label="发货状态" v-if="info.product_status !== 0">
            {{ info.product_status_name }}
          </st-info-item>
          <st-info-item label="操作时间">
            {{ info.operator_time }}
          </st-info-item>
        </st-info>
      </a-col>
    </a-row>
  </st-panel>
</section>
